description:
We have recently changed to passive staking - so until all Vampires are unstaked, holder count is incorrect.

[Website](https://svs.gg) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/SVSNFT) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/SVSNFT) | [IG](https://instagram.com/sneakyvampiresyndicate) | [Sneaky Vampiress Syndicate](https://opensea.io/collection/sneaky-vampiress-syndicate) | [Sneaky Bat Syndicate](https://opensea.io/collection/sneaky-bat-syndicate)

The Syndicate is known for its community, as they are staked to accrue their $BLOOD Tokens! Their furry friends in the form of Bat Companions never leave their side.

name: [ Ledger ] Market Pass - Genesis Edition
description:
[ Ledger ] Market is the most secure platform for artists and brands to release their NFTs, where Ledger customers can securely connect through Ledger Live and clear sign their transactions. For first access to exclusive collaborations, and Ledger hardware, software and services, become a [ Ledger ] Market Pass holder.


[ L ] Market’s brand mark is a generative font with over two billion unique variations. It speaks to: 1) the massive awareness generative art and PFP projects have brought to blockchain technology, and 2) the advanced cryptography built into Ledger and [ Ledger ] Market’s DNA.

name: WVRPS by WarpSound (Official)
description:
WVRPS are the 1st hybrid generative PFP + AI-composed music NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain. 9,999 unique NFTs based on the WarpSound virtual artists Nayomi, Gnar Heart + DJ Dragoon, with art by Emmy-winning illustrator Andy Poon, the embedded 1/1 original music composed entirely by AI using the visual traits of the PFP 🤯

WVRPS are the opening note of WarpSound’s larger vision for interactive, social music experience, helping ignite the future of generative music creativity + synthetic artistry. 🚀

https://warpsound.ai

name: Voxies
description:
Voxies are cute, lovable and collectible 3d voxel buddies, that live and play on the Ethereum blockchain. There are only 10,000 Voxies in existence and no two Voxies are identical. Lots of random properties and fun traits make each Voxie cute, unique and sometimes rare!

Voxies are not just a collectible but are also the first and only NFT to be fully integrated with a playable RPG turn-based tactical game. Bring your owned Voxies to life in Voxie Tactics as you collect, battle, and earn rewards in the Voxiverse. VOXEL tokens are used as the currency in Voxie Tactics and used to buy/trade on the Voxies marketplace.
